### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### Consultar regras
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/config/rules

### Registrar transacao suspeita
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_id": "ACC-100",
  "destination_account_id": "ACC-NEW",
  "amount": 25000,
  "currency": "BRL",
  "occurred_at": "2026-07-22T02:30:00Z",
  "destination_account_created_at": "2026-07-20T02:30:00Z"
}

### Listar suspeitas
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/transactions/suspicious
